event_name: Depin/Decentralized Storage Office Hours and Afternoon Social
description:
Take a pause from LabWeek with Banyan and Glif! We’re cohosting a coffee break to relax, mingle, and chat about the future of decentralized storage.

Why You should Come:
- Snag some snacks and warm beverages
- Learn more about Banyan’s approach to making Filecoin accessible to businesses and organizations with large storage needs.
- Learn more about borrowing FIL from GLIF - Filecoin’s premier DeFi protocol.
- Learn about Banyan’s SP program and how banyan can help you and your customers.
- Ask questions and share feedback.

RSVP and mark your calendars! See you in Istanbul!
